    <section class="steps-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-title">
                <h2>Simple 3-Step Process</h2>
                <p>Getting started with DropLaa is incredibly easy</p>
            </div>
            <div class="steps-grid">
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <h3>Upload Your Files</h3>
                    <p>Simply drag and drop your files into our secure upload area, or click to browse and select files from your device. We support all file types up to 10GB.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <h3>Get Your Share Link</h3>
                    <p>Once uploaded, you'll instantly receive a secure, unique link. Your files are encrypted and stored safely on our servers with bank-level security.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step-card">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <h3>Share & Track</h3>
                    <p>Share the link via email, social media, or any messaging platform. Track downloads and get notified when recipients access your files.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="video-section">
        <div class="container">
